Package java_gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionHandler
    The ActionHandler class manages the user interactions, order processing, and scene transitions within the application.
    Main
    The Main class serves as the entry point for the application.
    MainApplication
    This class sets up all JPanels used as scenes in the application.
    managerSql
    This class holds SQL queries and date parameters for managing reports and inventory in a store management system.
    OrderItem
    Represents an item in an order with a name and ID.
    OrderLogic
    Manages the logic for handling orders, including adding items, calculating prices, and interacting with the GUI.
